## 7) Production Hardening (Recommended Next)

1. Add model/version pinning so exact checkpoint is reproducible.
2. Add retries around STAC requests and item loading.
3. Reproject to a metric CRS before area computation for best geodetic accuracy.
4. Add unit tests:
   - bbox parser
   - cloud composite logic
   - area calculation.
5. Add Dockerfile and deploy API.

