## 8) Notes on Generalization Claim

To support your "generalization to South Asia delta complexity" claim, document:
1. Exact data window and bbox.
2. Model checkpoint and version hash.
3. Preprocessing/compositing method.
4. Comparative baseline (for example NDWI thresholding only).
5. Optional reference labels (Sen1Floods11/local annotated polygons) and metrics.

